    },
    {
      "type": "title",
      "source": "Enable All-Rounded Corner Note Pane",
      "target": "启用全圆角笔记面板"
    },
    {
      "type": "title",
      "source": "Enable sliding animation on main pane",
      "target": "为主面板启用滑动动画"
    },
    {
      "type": "description",
      "source": "Animation is noticable when you switch to a new tab",
      "target": "当您切换到新标签页时，动画效果会很明显。"
    },
    {
      "type": "title",
      "source": "Layout Section",
      "target": "布局部分"
    },
    {
      "type": "title",
      "source": "Enable Compact Tab Header",
      "target": "启用紧凑标签页标题"
    },
    {
      "type": "title",
      "source": "Enable Compact Tab Header (Stacked)",
      "target": "启用紧凑标签页标题（堆叠式）"
    },
    {
      "type": "description",
      "source": "If you noticed a broken gap after the toggle, just refresh it by clicking on the panes (so that they can readjust themselves).",
      "target": "如果您在切换后注意到有断裂的间隙，只需点击面板（以便它们可以重新调整自身）来刷新它。"
    },
    {
      "type": "title",
      "source": "Enable Overlay Scrollbar",
      "target": "启用覆盖滚动条"
    },
    {
      "type": "description",
      "source": "Overlay will provide you wider field of contents, but in return, scrollbar will have to overlap onto it.",
      "target": "覆盖层将为您提供更宽广的内容视野，但作为代价，滚动条将不得不覆盖在其上方。"
